reviews.text:
I am the owner.  Call now if you have any questions, 24 hours a day. No fee unless we win your case.

You pay insurance premiums, hoping you may never need to file a claim. Then during the time you need help most, the insurance company you hired to protect you takes your premium money and uses it against you.

I promise:

1.  To focus entirely on my clients;
2.  Aggressive representation by me and my staff;
3.  Immediate steps towards proper medical treatment and insurance coverage;
4.  Ease of access to me.  You can even have my cell phone number.
